        {
          "id": 592700,
          "key": "0393209e-3dbf-45f4-aa81-6e38b5b66a08",
          "title": "向量 - 数学定义",
          "semantic_type": "Concept",
          "is_public": true,
          "user_state": {
            "node_key": "0393209e-3dbf-45f4-aa81-6e38b5b66a08",
            "completed_at": null,
            "last_viewed_at": null,
            "unstructured": null
          },
          "resources": null,
          "atoms": [
            {
              "id": 592451,
              "key": "e5bffa21-4f39-4d15-8a98-e2919d1699e4",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 向量 - 数学定义 ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592452,
              "key": "26914a7e-5b20-4081-9924-40f12ea89e7d",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "什么是向量？简单解释下，向量是有序的数字列表。 \n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592453,
              "key": "8cfd07de-c5a3-4680-8424-376a88cd1b4e",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/January/5a6783cb_screen-shot-2018-01-23-at-10.49.16-am/screen-shot-2018-01-23-at-10.49.16-am.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/8cfd07de-c5a3-4680-8424-376a88cd1b4e",
              "caption": "_n 维向量_",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 80,
              "height": 150,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 592454,
              "key": "ff361dd0-e93c-486e-beb3-0726f6c92479",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "向量中的每个**元素**（亦称为**组件**或**坐标**）是一个数字，此处用 <span class=\"mathquill\">a_i</span> 表示。\n\n这个向量（上图中）有 <span class=\"mathquill\">n</span> 个元素，可以位于向量空间或是实数 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R}</span> 中。\n\n具有 <span class=\"mathquill\">n</span> 个真实元素的向量定义了 <span class=\"mathquill\">n</span> 维向量，属于向量空间 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R}^n</span>。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592455,
              "key": "8d311c5c-7ee4-4ade-9a46-e15b2caa3bfc",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "我们使用以下数学记法定义向量：<span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}</span>\n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592456,
              "key": "4b8f9775-618b-47fa-b820-04ed413fc99e",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "在上述示例中：\n-   向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}</span> 位于向量空间 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R}^n</span> 中。或者用数学记法表示为：<span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}\\in\\mathbb{R}^n</span>    \n\n\n-    <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}=\\begin{bmatrix} x_1\n\\\\ x_2\n\\\\ x_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\x_n\n\\end{bmatrix}</span>",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592457,
              "key": "59693e65-8962-494a-a6df-78b40192f260",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "和视频中一样，我们以更直观的方式讲解，并重点研究实数域<span class=\"mathquill\">2D</span>向量(即二维平面向量)。换句话说，我们将重点查看 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R}^2</span> 中的向量，该向量定义了平面上的所有点。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592458,
              "key": "71a239ac-1ec2-425d-8a03-5b42fdf4fa8c",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "我们来看看下图：",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592459,
              "key": "a99bbdfd-2998-48f7-be4e-7025662850e2",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/January/5a678d60_screen-shot-2018-01-23-at-11.30.13-am/screen-shot-2018-01-23-at-11.30.13-am.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/a99bbdfd-2998-48f7-be4e-7025662850e2",
              "caption": "",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 300,
              "height": 220,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 592460,
              "key": "31a13af0-d0ab-4f71-9f87-ddf5ae0e0f84",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "要从点 B 到点 A，我们需要向右走 4 步，再向上走 2 步。\n\n这样就定义了向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}=\\begin{bmatrix} \n4\n\\\\2\n\n\\end{bmatrix}</span>。 ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592461,
              "key": "eff6aed3-1f71-4633-8f94-c837d1bbee0c",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "下面的绿色箭头定义了向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}</span>。\n\n用图形表示时，我们使用箭头表示向量，如下图所示。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592462,
              "key": "10239b3a-b564-4c54-8abb-0063a05d614d",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/January/5a690865_screen-shot-2018-01-24-at-2.27.07-pm/screen-shot-2018-01-24-at-2.27.07-pm.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/10239b3a-b564-4c54-8abb-0063a05d614d",
              "caption": "",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 300,
              "height": 220,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 592463,
              "key": "ba760d25-c67f-4ad8-ad7b-24fc1d01ee3e",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "我们可以用角度或弧度来表示夹角，计算运动方向。在此实例中，我们采用弧度来表达（点击[此处](http://www.mathwarehouse.com/trigonometry/radians/convert-degee-to-radians.php)查看弧度与角度之间相互转换的计算公式）。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 592701,
          "key": "5fa5ca3b-15c9-4285-b69c-4e158ee8ef2b",
          "title": "转置",
          "semantic_type": "Concept",
          "is_public": true,
          "user_state": {
            "node_key": "5fa5ca3b-15c9-4285-b69c-4e158ee8ef2b",
            "completed_at": null,
            "last_viewed_at": null,
            "unstructured": null
          },
          "resources": null,
          "atoms": [
            {
              "id": 592464,
              "key": "4780ff1f-b4a7-4b62-b962-650ed7fb3848",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 向量转置",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592465,
              "key": "5d1feb83-d575-4162-916c-14d972d8165c",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "需要注意的是，在这节课中，我们重点讲解**列向量**。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592466,
              "key": "148d05b7-0ff1-4d6f-9d38-b97222327430",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}=\\begin{bmatrix} a_1\n\\\\ a_2\n\\\\ a_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\a_n\n\\end{bmatrix}</span> 是一个列向量。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592467,
              "key": "e8d281df-eef4-4a37-b437-2c6580d1b324",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "向量还可以表示为**行向量**。\n\n向量  <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{y}= \\begin{bmatrix}\n a_1&a_2  &a_3&  ...& a_n \n\\end{bmatrix}</span> 是行向量。\n\n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592468,
              "key": "3c3626bf-ef29-46ac-86bc-ee6376167f68",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "如果你仔细观察 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}</span> 和  <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{y}</span> 这两个向量，你会发现，它们的元素是一样的，只是一个排成列，一个排成行。 \n\n就好像一个向量倾斜了 <span class=\"mathquill\">90^{\\circ}</span>。\n\n在线性代数中，我们将这种变化称为**转置**。转置的数学符号是 <span class=\"mathquill\">T</span>，用法如下：\n ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592469,
              "key": "785bf10c-2f1b-4c0c-ad61-0f09dc542576",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": " <span class=\"mathquill\">\\begin{bmatrix} a_1\n\\\\ a_2\n\\\\ a_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\a_n\n\\end{bmatrix}^T=  \\begin{bmatrix}\n a_1&a_2  &a_3&  ...& a_n \n\\end{bmatrix}</span>\n\nOr:\n\n <span class=\"mathquill\"> \\begin{bmatrix}\n a_1&a_2  &a_3&  ...& a_n \n\\end{bmatrix}^T=\\begin{bmatrix} a_1\n\\\\ a_2\n\\\\ a_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\a_n\n\\end{bmatrix} </span> \n\n_方程 1_",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592470,
              "key": "49811f8f-5d9f-47bb-9c47-65706c09cffb",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "简言之：  \n\n<span class=\"mathquill\">\\large\\vec{x}^T=\\vec{y}</span>  \n\n 或\n\n <span class=\"mathquill\">\\large\\vec{y}^T=\\vec{x}</span>\n\n_方程 2_",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 592702,
          "key": "58c729f7-3b80-4259-abeb-327e1ec1d695",
          "title": "大小和方向",
          "semantic_type": "Concept",
          "is_public": true,
          "user_state": {
            "node_key": "58c729f7-3b80-4259-abeb-327e1ec1d695",
            "completed_at": null,
            "last_viewed_at": null,
            "unstructured": null
          },
          "resources": null,
          "atoms": [
            {
              "id": 592471,
              "key": "a65e0bf3-a192-41af-861f-23f2c072547f",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 大小和方向",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592472,
              "key": "badafc5a-13d3-4712-96bc-7acaeb215fd3",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "每个向量都包含运动的大小和方向。 \n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592473,
              "key": "84ec9fee-9707-40af-80c5-e2c5d2c6de59",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "我们来计算下向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}=\\begin{bmatrix} \n4\n\\\\2\n\n\\end{bmatrix}</span> 的大小和方向。\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592474,
              "key": "b10c1d9c-16ea-45a2-8de0-557cc8aa9d8b",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "**大小**的符号是 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\left \\|    \\right \\|</span>。\n\n要计算二维向量的**大小**，我们将使用[**勾股定理**](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pythagorean_theorem)（这个网址在国外，国内可能打不开）。\n\n在示例中，向量大小的计算方式如下所示：\n\n<span class=\"mathquill\">\\left \\|\\vec{x}  \\right \\|=\\sqrt{4^2+2^2}</span>\n\n其中 4 是向量的水平分量，2 是向量的垂直分量。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592475,
              "key": "7cad55ff-cf06-4f36-b679-270c75b277a6",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "要计算**运动方向**，我们将使用夹角。我们可以用度数或弧度来表示。在此示例中，我们将采用度数（我们始终可以[将度数转换为弧度，反之亦然](http://www.mathwarehouse.com/trigonometry/radians/convert-degee-to-radians.php)）。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592476,
              "key": "5fe6cb75-62ab-4db1-9cf3-017408b4ccb9",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "我们再次看看向量 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}</span>。它与水平轴的夹角为 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\theta</span>。 \n\n请看下图： ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592477,
              "key": "3a8a95de-ea9f-46b9-adee-598c04396531",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/January/5a691f30_screen-shot-2018-01-24-at-3.13.49-pm/screen-shot-2018-01-24-at-3.13.49-pm.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/3a8a95de-ea9f-46b9-adee-598c04396531",
              "caption": "",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 300,
              "height": 220,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 592478,
              "key": "717e159c-955d-4ac9-bb3b-9cb54da472fe",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "要计算 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\theta</span>，我们将运用三角学知识！\n\n对于下图中表示的夹角 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\theta</span>，计算方式如下所示：\n\n<span class=\"mathquill\">\\theta=tan^{-1}\\frac{y}{x}</span> \n\n_方程 3_",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592479,
              "key": "290e6fb4-61a5-4948-bf18-db5f84fe5634",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/March/5ab2d176_screen-shot-2018-03-21-at-2.40.42-pm/screen-shot-2018-03-21-at-2.40.42-pm.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/290e6fb4-61a5-4948-bf18-db5f84fe5634",
              "caption": "",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 300,
              "height": 220,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 592480,
              "key": "0d46fc8d-40d2-4666-bfbc-96b0f698b3c2",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "因此，在我们的示例中\n\n  <span class=\"mathquill\">\\theta=tan^{-1}\\frac{2}{4}=26.56505^{\\circ}</span> ",
