              "key": "2688f8dc-fdf7-4aa3-b3ff-811e9033ec4c",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 向量加法",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592494,
              "key": "cdfa5159-2fe5-44b9-9798-b6edb0779a05",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "\n<span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R^n}</span> **向量加法**的数学定义是逐个将元素相加。 \n\n我们来看看下面两个向量示例：",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592495,
              "key": "07815dfd-5691-49f2-b501-365d1c6a6acc",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "\n-  <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}=\\begin{bmatrix} a_1\n\\\\ a_2\n\\\\ a_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\a_n\n\\end{bmatrix}\\in\\mathbb{R^n}</span>\n\n\n-  <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix} b_1\n\\\\ b_2\n\\\\ b_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\b_n\n\\end{bmatrix}\\in\\mathbb{R^n}</span>\n\n\n",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592496,
              "key": "8bdd8c6f-1111-4868-ad4a-6fcfb91b6595",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "结果 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}+\\vec{y}</span> 将位于相同的实数域 <span class=\"mathquill\">\\mathbb{R^n}</span>。\n\n从数学角度：",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592497,
              "key": "16e95f94-0268-4265-974b-d93186f50d99",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "<span class=\"mathquill\">\\vec{x}+\\vec{y}=\\begin{bmatrix} a_1+b_1\n\\\\ a_2+b_2\n\\\\ a_3+b_3\n\\\\ :\n\\\\a_n+b_n\n\\end{bmatrix}\\in\\mathbb{R^n}</span>\n\n_方程 4_",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            }
          ]
        },
