              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 练习 1 的答案",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592522,
              "key": "6b5fe976-88eb-483b-a9db-7109ed7e6f78",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "向量的大小是：\n\n<span class=\"mathquill\">\\sqrt{a^2+b^2+c^2} </span>。\n\n\n在 workspace 中需要使用以下格式：`\\sqrt{a^2+b^2+c^2}`。",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592523,
              "key": "e146e974-3462-4cc0-b226-ce11a37dd144",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 练习 2 的答案",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592524,
              "key": "06ba0714-41fc-4161-82d9-922217c5e3ab",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "算出加法结果后，可视化向量。绘出图形后，你将发现很容易就能找到答案。 \n\n- 大小：<span class=\"mathquill\">1</span> \n- 方向：<span class=\"mathquill\">0{^\\circ}</span>（请在 workspace 填写 <span class=\"mathquill\">0</span>） ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592525,
              "key": "5c98402f-d6ab-4513-8a02-e663dd5c8cbf",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# 练习 3 的答案",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 592526,
              "key": "43560040-9027-4e3d-ab80-1cbac4ce2f40",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": " (a) 大小现在是：\n\n<span class=\"mathquill\">|\\alpha|\\sqrt{a^2 + b^2}</span>.\n\n在 workspace 中需要使用以下格式：`\\alpha\\sqrt{a^2 + b^2}`。\n\n (b) 方向会改变吗？\n\n不会\n\n (c) 方向将改变 <span class=\"mathquill\">180{^\\circ}</span> \n\n（仅在 workspace 填写 <span class=\"mathquill\">180</span>）\n\n\n\n(d) 大小将\n\n**减小**",
